27/06/2006
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- US Ambassador to Sofia John R. Beyrle said on Tuesday (27 June) that he expects the agreement on US military bases in Bulgaria to bring real benefits to the Bulgarian economy, in addition to strengthening bilateral political and military ties. Speaking at a forum dedicated to economic and trade opportunities related to the agreement, Beyrle cited job creation and potential contracts for Bulgarian companies in future procurement tenders. (BNR, BTA - 27/06/06) 
